565
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,760
Astaga!

566
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:35,719
Mungkin sebaiknya meneguk...

567
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,000
Sangat indah.

568
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:54,560
Lihat...

569
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:56,719
Bahkan sebuah bintang pun jatuh menimpaku.

570
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,880
Apakah itu benar-benar jatuh?

571
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,280
Aduh...

572
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,120
Tuan Klao ada di sana!

573
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:52,240
